collectionMetadata.name: ASEAN architects registered under BOA
collectionMetadata.description: Listing of architects who are ASEAN architects currently registered under the Board of Architects. An ASEAN architect is a person who is registered, licensed or professionally recognised as an architect in ASEAN. The Association of Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN) is a regional intergovernmental organisation comprising 10 countries in Southeast Asia. For more information on registration and about the ASEAN architect, go to http://www.boa.gov.sg and http://m.aseanarchitectcouncil.org
